{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/custom-variables/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"CSS para impacientes"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"753d8f2b-2756-5613-84c3-dd908006e900","excerpt":"CSS variables that contain specific values to be reused throughout a document. Explanation The variables are defined globally within the  CSS pseudo-class which…","html":"<p>CSS variables that contain specific values to be reused throughout a document.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>custom-variables<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>CSS is awesome!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">:root</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* Place variables within here to use the variables globally. */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.custom-variables</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">--some-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #da7800<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">--some-keyword</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> italic<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">--some-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1.25em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">--some-complex-value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px 1px 2px whitesmoke<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0 0 1em slategray<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0 0 0.2em slategray<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--some-color<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--some-size<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--some-keyword<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--some-complex-value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h4>Explanation</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>The variables are defined globally within the <code class=\"language-text\">:root</code> CSS pseudo-class which matches the root element of a tree representing the document. Variables can also be scoped to a selector if defined within the block.</li>\n<li>Declare a variable with <code class=\"language-text\">--variable-name:</code>.</li>\n<li>Reuse variables throughout the document using the <code class=\"language-text\">var(--variable-name)</code> function.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Browser support</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://caniuse.com/#feat=css-variables\">https://caniuse.com/#feat=css-variables</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"http://github.com/30-seconds/\">Acesse a Referência original</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Custom variables","date":"January 04, 2020","description":""}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/custom-variables/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/disable-selection/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Disable selection"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/custom-text-selection/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Custom text selection"}}}}}